name: Tyrian
description:
What is Tyrian?

Tyrian is a beautiful general model for creating a lot of images, especially portraits, characters, landscapes and sceneries. Like most models, it is not perfect and may have flaws, but the inpainting model of this can fix it (download separately.) Also, use this model within the boundaries of legalities, for you will be responsible for everything and not the author of this model.

If you like what I do, your support is much appreciated.

Use the default settings, or the settings you like best. As for the prompts, use the standards. Thank you for patronizing my model.
